Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.00,Asteroid - staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}翻译:univer  MF    校对＆压制:CZ    时轴:aho    后期:CZ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:23.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小的时候  我参加了镇上的露营活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,与一名小男孩相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:29.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你在这儿做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我在平息自己的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,露营地的光会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:54.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是木星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:56.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:00:59.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看  在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是个点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:06.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然用双眼望远镜看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,木星是有着条纹的  并且戴着一个细细的环
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:17.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,类似月球的卫星有七十多个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你真是见多识广呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,变星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:27.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,转学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:29.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:33.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,变星米拉  位于鲸鱼座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是颗亮度会变化的不可思议的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害  我和星星名字一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那蓝呢  有叫蓝的星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有  那么怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:47.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,才不怪呢  很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,再说如果没有的话  去取一个不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,取一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小行星的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果发现了应该是可以命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就去寻找那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:04.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在那之后  再也没有见过那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:16.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,成为高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能与大家一起在同一个学校学习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我感到非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,面向各自的梦想与目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一同相互勤勉  共同进步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天开始就是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,入学后就准备要做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:43.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃  去年还在的天文部没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明都已经决定进高中后绝对要进的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,啊  关于那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你是…远藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天文部今年和地质研合并了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,变为地科部了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地科部？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是没想到社团竟然合并了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:08.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为没什么人气？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,才没这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去年的文化祭都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这儿是性感天象仪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还非常热闹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这难道不就是原因么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,文化祭被训话的那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嘛  先放一边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,被训了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:31.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,部员减少  以及其他一些大人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:36.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为同属地学科  就和地质研合为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:43.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯…望天上和看地面  感觉完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在宇宙上看的话哪边不都一样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃  银河一般的视角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,快住手  多害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:59.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个…部室是不是有点远？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是文化部里最靠里面的场地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,建筑是不是有点旧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍  稍微有点漏风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不过漏雨的问题已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  我把参观者带来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天  地  人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是战争吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,应该不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  刚刚才合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们也还没有适应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是部长森野  原天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是副部长樱井哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我原来是地质研的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,于是呢  哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哪边…是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质与天文  你想入哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是加入地质班的话  竟然还会赠送新生限定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以提升运气的能量石头套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长  这样做部员又会减少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  副部长太在意人数经费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是二年级的猪濑  也是地质班的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是一年级的真中  想加入天文班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也有新生诶  我也是准备加入天文班的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:22.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以及我有件事情想要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想要发现小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  还真是远大的目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这不是很难的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然之前也有高中生发现的案例
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像我们这样弱小的社团基本上不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长  这个说法太严苛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  但是我下过约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以前跟一个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  从来没听你说过啊米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:58.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是说了的话  小铃肯定会去调查那个男孩的身世的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯  彻查到底  名字搞快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:01.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:07.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们约定好了  一起寻找小行星  然后将它取名为蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是在那之后就没见过那个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  那个人莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不用莫非了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,脸  变通红了哦  真中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真中蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝是那个蓝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来是女孩子么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟名字很像男的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,头发也很短
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在那之后我也一直想着要找到小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难道说是为了不忘记我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,会变得有趣起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个时候遇到的男孩  原来是女孩子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,===op===
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.99,Asteroid - title,,0,0,0,,{\fs83\pos(515,911)\fad(1000,1000)\3c&H5F2830&\3a&HFF&\4c&HAC8991&\4a&HFF&}二人的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天真是吃了一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到竟然是同一个高中同一个部的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能够再会非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,把你当成男孩了真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今后也多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍微借我书看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.02,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,书名：不会失败的商业邮件写法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,准备要打工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:16.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:19.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:24.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一直想念着憧憬着的她  好不容易能再次见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,憧憬什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难得见到小铃这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:35.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明只要有人接近我一直都显得不高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:39.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事啦  因为真中同学是女生  而且还很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对方是女生的话完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:45.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯  很僵硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,过去明明更加率直呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我是不是做了什么被她讨厌的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,唯一要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,发太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在意的话就去当面谈谈好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不想太多就付诸行动  也是米菈的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还是稍微熟虑一下呗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,啊有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝  午饭一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  米菈一下就冲进教室里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:32.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝  抱歉昨晚给你发了一堆信息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.37,0:10:36.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,很困扰的吧  以后我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没  没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全没有感到困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,发不来可爱的回复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:52.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃以前开始就是那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝跟小时候的气质完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,野营的时候觉得真是个健谈的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,现在变得很成熟  冰山美人的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,等…米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我稍微去洗洗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能多学学真中同学的稳重就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…完全不稳重的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,语言能力不足  而且总是会慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在米菈的面前也是害怕失败很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,害怕失败是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:40.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以前因为说错话  留下了羞愧的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好热  今天总觉得按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小蓝  要说的话应该是汗流浃背
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小蓝刚刚说了色色的词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小蓝  好色色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那之后  就不太擅长和别人说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,直接性格都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说到语言能力  米菈才是真的没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:09.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,身为青梅竹马的我都这么说了  那一定就没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:13.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下来你们两要一起寻找小行星对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:17.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:22.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,既然有着相同的梦想  关系一定会很快变好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:27.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃  这个怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用手帕一点一点擦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,铃明明都那么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还是好不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,跟小时候的气质完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,头发变长也长高了  话也变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,确实和那时候的感觉不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  刚才找到了好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的是好东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝  现在你能看见外边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,西边的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是水星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我受到了你的影响学了很多哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:35.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事的  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:44.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉突然给你打电话  而且也不是有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全没事的  我们来聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,聊天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说话说  现在能看见金星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:14:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个时候  黎明看应该能看见很亮的金星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,亮度差不多是负4等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉你很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,昨天和蓝聊了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝一点都不高冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,超级可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,班会要开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,第一回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地科部会议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,活动内容还没明确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:15:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想着先把大家想做的事和想要的东西整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Heavy\bord0\c&H17120C&\pos(1331.2,161.6)}直径30米望远镜计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,刚才不是说想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,部里预算有限  要在这个范围内考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,预算大概有多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就算你们摆出这个表情  预算也不会增加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟天文部和地质研都没什么实绩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,参加比赛  获过大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像这样活跃的部预算就比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:36.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果想要买高级望远镜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:39.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说要认真活动  拿出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比起这个  我们何时来BBQ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小铃不入部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说是要帮家里做事会很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那孩子要是参加了地质班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,各班三人  人数就平衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:07.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打起精神来  我会一个顶两个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪濑  你的反复横跳真的很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暂且先把在合并之前的活动列了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,设备也有  活动大多能照常进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最大的问题就是最花钱的合宿和文化祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说到文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:30.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们的那个  今年不会做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不用拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明是高中生  却走性感路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也太不知廉耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,明明这么有人气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其实副部长从去年一直在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用cosplay吸引客人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我觉得就应该像我们一样认真办展会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,结果客人是天文部的十分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪濑  你话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:07.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉分歧太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,确实完全没有两班一起活动的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉要有才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,共同活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:25.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一起做之前的活动还是想些新的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们怎么觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么你们的话彼此都能懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像心灵感应一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  我有一个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,两班协同制作会刊怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,会刊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:45.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没错  制作介绍我们活动的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,会刊有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:56.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去年的文化节  虽然客人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但我觉得展会真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以  我觉得要是提升了社团的知名度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:06.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说不定就会有更多的人来看展会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪猪学姐  会刊是什么都能写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪猪学姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只要是关于部里活动的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我要是关于小行星的介绍的  感觉能写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是创立了有趣的板区的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说不定会有更多的人对我们产生兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那么我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就做介绍矿物的版区
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不错呢  那杂志名取什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,周刊「寻找小行星」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每回附赠望远镜小部件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,驳回  太偏向天文班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,周刊的话好像不太行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,附录也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那副部长觉得什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad3\fn方正舒体_GBK\4c&H7E6191&\c&H4C4352&\frz4.749\pos(845.334,488)}Mica Time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正稚艺_GBK\bord0\shad2\c&H42B2B2&\frz3.529\pos(828,826.667)}云母{\fs60\c&H97525B&}克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正稚艺_GBK\frz7.045\bord0\c&H5340A0&\b1\pos(848.381,978.096)}创刊号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就  「寻找吧！小行星」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们  很有勇气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要统一起来真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但很有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉在兴头上的时候打扰你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,放学时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那就「天地创造」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,更可爱一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可爱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要吃汉堡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,星星好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然还是要能够传达出石头魅力的名字好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:48.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长  边吃汉堡边再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,肚子饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,Kirakira？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟星星和石头都很闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不会很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有  特别可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,超炫超nice的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,炫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪濑  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我一直都在想怎么认真地开展活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:25.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然还是得让更多人知道我们的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:32.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  为此我们需要先降低门槛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:37.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个计划怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.26,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康POP1体W5\fs45\bord0\c&H707E85&\pos(1400,732.8)}不输给天文班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.26,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑體 TW Heavy\fs70\bord0\c&H585C61&\pos(1444.8,958.4)}超性感石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这点笨拙的地方又…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么样  大家相处的融洽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:50.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱井对不熟的人总是傲傲的  有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,猪濑在中间调剂  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,活动计划  我加一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,替我转告大家  下周末腾出时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,无论如何都要办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个时间  冬天的星座还很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:26.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像这样和蓝聊着天看着星星  真的有些不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和蓝能够再会  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:34.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,心中一直盼望着  希望有一天能够再遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那么明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:47.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:55.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:00.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,两个人许下的诺言
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:38.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,下回  河滩的银河
